room_title: Escape room "The Shack" by Mystery Chambers in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_address: 654 Main St NW Elk River, MN 55330
room_description: Every year, your friend Henry the Hunter invites you to his hunting shack for the great deer hunt. Every year Henry ups his game in the quality of practical jokes he plays on his guests. This year is no different. You have received the customary invite to attend but he promises to up the ante. Are you up to the challenge?
